Dear Students and residents,

The Voluntary Blood and Eye Donor's Club, IIT Madras conducts Blood Donatio
n Camps periodically to motivate students and campus residents into this ac
tivity. The club also arranges donors to hospitals in Chennai during emerge
ncy situations. The camps are conducted in association with Voluntary Healt
h Services (VHS) Chennai. This semester's camp will be conducted as follows
.

Venue : Students Activity Center (SAC)
Date   : 2nd October, 2016 (Sunday)
Time   : 9.00 am  12.30 pm

 PLEASE HAVE BREAKFAST BEFORE YOU COME TO DONATE BLOOD.
 We only use disposable equipment.
 You can resume your normal work immediately after donation.
 Blood Typing is done free of cost for donors.

Regards
Voluntary Blood and Eye Donors' Club, IIT Madras
